action.description: Passed Second Reading as amended in HD 1; placed on the calendar for Third Reading with Representative(s) Matsumoto, Reyes Oda, Shimizu voting aye with reservations; Representative(s) Alcos, Garcia, Muraoka, Pierick, Souza voting no (5) and Representative(s) Cochran, Hussey, Lowen, Ward excused (4).
